Project to build a SBC powered system that is using excess solar electricity
to heat water.

# confuguration steps
Load default configution of desired SBC (RPI3)
    make raspberrypi3_defconfig

Configure system
    make menuconfig
      Build options  --->
        ($(TOPDIR)/configs/shw_defconfig) Location to save buildroot config
      System configuration  --->
        (swh) System hostname
        (Welcome to the solar water heater) System banner
        (raspberry) Root password
      Target packages  --->
        Interpreter languages and scripting  --->
          [*] python3
        Text editors and viewers  --->
          [*] nano
        Networking applications  --->
          [*] dropbear
        Filesystem and flash utilities  --->
          [*] nfs-utils

# TODO
nfs
app

Save configuration
    make savedefconfig

# build procedure
First step is to clone and define the latest stable branch (2307)
    git clone git@github.com:brenkem/solar-water-heater.git
    git checkout 2023.05.x

Load custom config
    make shw_defconfig

Build firmware
    make
